    • Constructor Detail

      • CodeElement

        public CodeElement(java.lang.String name,
                   CodeParent parent,
                   CodeVisibility visibility,
                   boolean isAbstract,
                   boolean isStatic,
                   boolean isFinal)
        Constructor with name, CodeParent and modifiers.
        The modifiers are converted to an int value usable for the CodeModifier methods.
        Initializes the lists of CodeFields, CodeConstructors, CodeMethods, CodeTemplateBindings, CodeTemplateParameters and nested CodeElements.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the element
        parent - the CodeParent of the element
        visibility - the CodeVisibility value representing the access modifier of the element
        isAbstract - determines whether the element is abstract
        isStatic - determines whether the element is static
        isFinal - determines whether the element is final
